Architecture Overview

    1. Component Structure
        - Rust/WASM Core
            - Timeline management (clips, tracks)
            - Export orchestration
            - Audio waveform calculation
            - Thumbnail generation logic
        - TypeScript Frontend
            - Editor UI (React/Vue)
            - WebCodecs video encoding
            - FFmpeg.wasm integration
            - Canvas-based preview renderer

    2. Data Flow
        - User interactions → TypeScript → Rust/WASM (processing) → TypeScript (rendering)
        - Media files → FFmpeg.wasm → Processed assets → WebCodecs → Final output
